Natural fruits and herbs are high in nutritional value and are essentially used by consumers to help maintain a healthy diet. Whether the goal is to reduce unwanted fats, stimulate blood flow and pressure, balance PH levels, or encourage fertility in women. The list of benefits can go on forever tbh. Of course, my opinion is always biased towards my homeland. In Jamaica is where you will get the best in fresh fruits, vegetables, and herbs. 
No disrespect to the wholesale and supermarkets, but I prefer to get my provisions from the street vendors. My grandmother used to sell oranges at the bus stop when I was a school girl. On these same streets. In the hot sun 🥵 So, I support our local vendors, and I support our local farmers. You should, too. Or just grow them yourselves... 😏🇯🇲 #HealthIsWealth #Lasvegasbrunchwknd2023

This is not a prank. God made a way so we could make the best decision. We now own THREE properties, enough for each of our kids to have one of their own. As soon as I stopped going hard for people, I was able to enjoy investing more in the family I created. My son and my daughter will depend on NO ONE. That is my best kept PROMISE. Growing up I never had hand-outs or inheritance to back me up or keep me afloat. Most of my life I've acquired things that resemble success but I could never really feel successful because I was still in survival mode. Nobody's dream is mine, and my dream doesn't have to be yours. Real life is sink or swim. Do what YOU can to provide all the life-jackets necessary for your family, but my kids.....they will own the very same waters that almost drowned me. As with everything else, this is for them...🙏🏽

Happy Sunday u guys 🤍
At my lowest, God brought me up. At my highest I brought God with me...✨️
